{"tid":2134677,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：跟「燒山」玩Patreon為法治重生抗爭  戴耀廷變KOL吸千人課金 - 李八方","createTime":"2020-08-01T01:47:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-01T03:06:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"676fb20c052c181c0dce0e8b6a13f632f1558b4f","tid":2134677,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T01:47:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200731/ML52SD37OOTE3H5HYWGW27UVW4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200731%2FML52SD37OOTE3H5HYWGW27UVW4%2F&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOWyAt0yGCUsyxQooKadsmXE%3D&h=e1b12184\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200731%2FML52SD37OOTE3H5HYWGW27UVW4%2F&h=95f4ec54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200731/ML52SD37OOTE3H5HYWGW27UVW4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：跟「燒山」玩Patreon為法治重生抗爭 <br />\n戴耀廷變KOL吸千人課金 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/E-JtY9hC8f-bQwKdrqaQFwjhMWU=/737x554/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4KDGBT6PWA4TMBW5WNMPQBIOPM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FE-JtY9hC8f-bQwKdrqaQFwjhMWU%3D%2F737x554%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4KDGBT6PWA4TMBW5WNMPQBIOPM.jpg&h=a86b2828&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n畀左報攻擊為「戴妖」嘅港大法律學院前副教授戴耀廷，自從話唔再搞民主派選舉協調，呢個星期又俾一班港大校委無視程序公義通過炒魷，戴教授之後回應話呢個結果係意料之內，仲話雖然離開港大嘅崗位，但佢對法治嘅研究同教學工作唔會停落嚟。呢頭講完，佢已經坐言起行，星期三開咗Patreon賬戶，開宗名義講「為香港法治的重生而繼續抗爭」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n月捐者可同戴耀廷傾偈<br />\n<br />\n講到Patreon呢個網上平台嘅KOL，人稱「燈神」、「燒山」嘅蕭若元算係大家熟悉嘅成功個案，佢擁有接近2.6萬個訂戶；戴耀廷就一日多啲吸引到過千人課金，走勢非常凌厲。<br />\n<br />\n八方睇過戴耀廷開設咗三級課金方案，入門級。。。。。。。。。。仲有機會出埋力，有機會為香港法治而戰。<br />\n<br />\n李八方"},{"pid":"4a2e67fdc27b56d380d0afb094f4932d7c90fcfa","tid":2134677,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T02:57:29.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d53430cf609a6011e86804a2f0bd00570102cd92","tid":2134677,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:02:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/bennytai\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fbennytai&d=dD36If%2FKkPZsb%2F00sEqzOWyAt0yGCUsyxQooKadsmXE%3D&h=0639e1bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/bennytai</a>"},{"pid":"a84af6421b82b0ebfc26688cc64fba347236f11e","tid":2134677,"uid":10520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-01T03:06:35.000Z","msg":"老少做慈善事業，梗係需要錢啦"}]}